<step1>
<ptxt>ACTIVE TEST</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname="C131977E01" width="2.775699831in" height="2.775699831in"/>
</figure>
<ptxt>Performing the ACTIVE TEST using the intelligent tester allows the meters, indicators and so on to operate without parts removal. Performing the ACTIVE TEST as the first step of troubleshooting is one way to save diagnostic time. It is possible to display the DATA LIST on the intelligent tester during the ACTIVE TEST.</ptxt>
<step2>
<ptxt>Connect the intelligent tester to the DLC3.</ptxt>
</step2>
<step2>
<ptxt>Turn the engine switch on (IG).</ptxt>
</step2>
<step2>
<ptxt>Enter the following menus: DIAGNOSIS / OBD /MOBD / METER / ACTIVE TEST.</ptxt>
</step2>
